{"tid":492684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警官爬高探頭監視同袍：「X你老味X，你有冇喺入邊食煙！」","createTime":"2017-12-07T18:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T01:41:33.000Z","uid":70985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dab9f59c29258e4e0cf7ea9757fd1d2f700ce389","tid":492684,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T18:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171207/large/1512660767_1522.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171207%2Flarge%2F1512660767_1522.png&h=4f098ea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長沙灣警署爆出懷疑侵犯私隱風波。有現役警員向《蘋果》投訴，指該署有高層為打擊警署內違規吸煙情況，涉嫌在更衣室爬高探頭監視在廁格內如廁的警員。據悉，有警員上月在廁格內大便時，赫然發現被高層探頭監視，兩人四目交投後，涉事高層以粗口辱罵「X你老味X，你有冇喺入邊食煙！」警方回應指會作跟進。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該高層近日不時親自到更衣室巡察，偷看同袍大便一事更在警署內廣為流傳。駐守長沙灣警署的警員陳先生（化名）稱，曾向受害事主查證，確認事件在署內5樓男更衣室發生，署內不少基層員工脅於高層權威，均敢怒不敢言。<br />\n他指，各警署向來也有違規吸煙情況，「你捉食煙係啱，但唔係咁樣捉囉，完全係侵犯私隱。」他又指，受害警員當時根本沒在廁格內吸煙，「唔知佢（涉事高層）係唔係聞到煙味，咁樣伸個頭入去（廁格）裝，畀人發現都唔道歉，仲要用粗口鬧人。」<br />\n陳估計，事件或與署內人事鬥爭有關，「佢（涉事高層）個職位本應淨係做行政，紀律問題係其他人負責，但佢近排就周圍捉人食煙，唔知係唔係想做畀上面睇。」他稱，據他了解，已有數名同袍被涉事高層即場「斷正」，「畀佢揸正嚟做，上庭罰1,500蚊、仲要紀律處分。」<br />\n本報向警察公共關係科查詢上述事件、以及在該署違規吸煙被控的警員數字等，對方未有正面回應，只稱警方重視人員的操守及個人私隱，會了解跟進事件；又重申根據警察通例，除指揮官特定劃作吸煙區的地點外，任何人不得在警署內吸煙，違規警員會被檢控及紀律處分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171208/57554339\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F57554339&d=W%2Bs0AQgvD%2Bcf6t2x4TcuGghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=d8f28099\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F57554339&h=f246b982\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171208/57554339</a>"},{"pid":"bc87fec713bfd36e0bbb61ceca2a342e9c09100d","tid":492684,"uid":49392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T19:02:06.000Z","msg":"醉翁之意唔係捉人食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a640a601f808948519232725e35e73297b095916","tid":492684,"uid":82621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T19:05:07.000Z","msg":"[url]長沙灣警署警員廁格大便  赫然發現被高層探頭監視 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/492630/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/492630/page/1?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n有人post左了"},{"pid":"827cd13eae3f592d6bd29197aa636ba4a1bf47b7","tid":492684,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T19:06:58.000Z","msg":"自膠先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826748a4b812849496495bf79f83e30837a9dcf7","tid":492684,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:03:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9bb7595b379c6b2b3ebba034c86fa6143b52fd3","tid":492684,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:23:08.000Z","msg":"性騷擾？"},{"pid":"cf1e9bf8667d09297671741ad2b17f077be2fb21","tid":492684,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:26:14.000Z","msg":"佢閒到既真係煙味? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb2bccf9869e9421d06e5a4f41c4e2cc274d2c2","tid":492684,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:26:34.000Z","msg":"對待爛仔係咁嘅方法㗎啦"},{"pid":"b36d90170d3250c460d7e7317d33686a6e20014b","tid":492684,"uid":34498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:28:06.000Z","msg":"聞到碌鳩味要快啲捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04f9fe27f61dbcac68192906a3f2a55e03447af","tid":492684,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:29:11.000Z","msg":"警犬真係日日都有on9野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ed56de1038eccceb64903a3444f33b784ac712","tid":492684,"uid":3